Key Match Events: Yves Bissouma scored the winning goal for Mali in the seventh minute after a defensive blunder by Eswatini.
Moussa Djenepo from Mali had to be replaced by Camara after a heavy collision with Mpendulo Tfomo from Eswatini in the 12th minute.
Adama Malouda Traore missed a chance for Mali in the 28th minute with a shot over the bar.
Salim Diakite's low cross in the 36th minute went through Mamadou Doumbia, who could not reach the ball with the goalkeeper already out of his line.
Mohamed Camara wasted a chance for Mali with a weak shot from outside the box.
Yves Bissouma missed an opportunity to set up a second goal for Mali in the 55th minute.
Adama Malouda had another chance in the 62nd minute but his shot went wide of the right post.
